a little lunch for Steve.

05:46.435 --> 05:47.645
That was thoughtful.

05:47.770 --> 05:49.647
How was "Coffee with the Principal"?

05:49.772 --> 05:51.850
He made a scene!
He told Principal Lewis

05:51.975 --> 05:53.384
I should be getting better grades,

05:53.509 --> 05:56.220
then he went to my classes,
got a week's worth of homework,

05:56.345 --> 05:57.941
and made me study till midnight.

05:58.107 --> 05:59.317
That sounds fantastic.

05:59.483 --> 06:00.959
Here, take your lunch.
No time to dilly.

06:01.084 --> 06:02.360
The bus is running
three minutes early.

06:02.485 --> 06:03.655
Go, go, go, go, go.

06:03.821 --> 06:07.264
Wow. Roger really seems
to be on top of things.

06:07.389 --> 06:08.600
