08:14.806 --> 08:16.412
Oh, no you don't.
Roger!

08:16.578 --> 08:17.651
Lewis, this is Roger Smith.

08:17.776 --> 08:19.707
I need you to stop calling my boy.

08:19.873 --> 08:21.321
